<font color="#FF0000">MEATBALL AND A GLASS OF WATER?</font><br>
<tt>Thu Nov 13 22:54:57 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Geez...all I was trying to do was to get him to try sumptin besides pizza.<br>
He kept bothering the waitress for some parmesian cheese for his won ton soup...and some olives to dip in his sweet and sour sauce.(he brought his own aged wine..Thunderbird...early November 97!)<br>
Hell, I even took &quot;Toon Sarge&quot; with me to take the focus off DZ..God was I embarrassed...finally asked the waitress to move me to the Officer's section.  It was a big change..they had bowls, plates...flat ware etc.<br>
Ordered Dented Zippo and Toon Sarge a bowl of soup.. neither one could empty their bowls (drooled more back in than they dipped out!)<br>
Neither had any trouble draining their finger bowls.. one gulp and it was all gone.  TS protested that his finger bowl didn't have any fingers just juice.  All I could think of was &quot;Airborne, all the way... drop and give me fifty!&quot;  It seemed to calm him down.<br>
Finally slipped Mama San some MPC and low crawled out into the parking lot to avoid being stared at...DZ and TS seemed to hit it off pretty good.  Of Course they share a lot of common ground... both being humanoid challenged and severly retarded.  <br>
A little old lady helped me cross the street.. she commended me for feeding the animals.<br><br>
All in all Mom would have been proud of me.. only stole one ashtray!<br><br>
MTF - Messhall Training Foray<br><br>
P.S.  Where is Slobbering Warrior when I need him?<br><br>

